## Method

### Overview

We design a **Script Compiler Agent System** that generates fully runnable Python pipeline scripts for AI video production (based on your existing `08_ultra_director.py` and `09_viral_factory.py`).

Instead of manually writing pipeline code, you will provide a **Creative Input Pack**, and the system outputs a **ready-to-run .py script** with all prompts, scene logic, and execution flow embedded.

